_sText:
This is my first Gun Game map. I went through several level designs to find out what makes a good gun game map.

Turns it simplicity is the key, this map is beautifully presented with that note in mind.


Size: Small

Players: 10 - 22



Map created by me, textures created by me.

It's in .pak so no need to download any textures, they're embedded in the map.

I plan to make more in a similar fashion. Please tell me what you think!
